author: Tony Garcia | agarcia6@mlive.com
title: Twenty years after meeting in bowling alley, Coldwater couple each roll 300 game on same day
text: "It was just a casual sort of Sunday thing," Brian said. "We hadn't bowled together in a long time, and I said, 'Hey, let's do it' and this is what happened. None of it was expected, it's just one of those things where everything lined up that day."
